1
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:39,020
=Love Beyond the Grave=

2
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:40,660
(Diadaptasi daripada novel "Love Beyond the Grave",
karya Li Qingran)

3
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,990
=Episod 21=

4
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:55,390
Ketumbar kegemaran awak.

5
00:01:56,300 --> 00:01:57,140
Saya tak faham

6
00:01:57,140 --> 00:01:58,190
macam mana awak boleh suka bau ini.

7
00:02:01,030 --> 00:02:01,870
Wanginya.

8
00:02:04,990 --> 00:02:05,830
Awak tak suka?

9
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:17,420
Simu,

10
00:02:17,950 --> 00:02:19,700
bukan kita sudah janji
nak hidup macam orang biasa

11
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:21,460
dan tidak guna kuasa roh?

12
00:02:25,790 --> 00:02:26,630
Cepatlah makan.

13
00:02:38,350 --> 00:02:39,190
Simu,

14
00:02:39,950 --> 00:02:41,300
kini tujuh belas negeri
sudah ditawan semula,

15
00:02:42,550 --> 00:02:43,700
awak juga bukan lagi Penguasa Roh.

16
00:02:44,420 --> 00:02:45,260
Seterusnya,

17
00:02:45,990 --> 00:02:47,070
kita akan menetap di sini.

18
00:02:47,420 --> 00:02:48,260
Bagaimana?

19
00:02:49,550 --> 00:02:50,390
Baiklah.

20
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:20,580
Rasanya kehidupan sebegini

21
00:03:21,510 --> 00:03:22,460
baik juga.

22
00:03:26,790 --> 00:03:27,630
Duan Shunxi,

23
00:03:29,230 --> 00:03:30,550
saya suka bersama dengan awak.

24
00:03:39,350 --> 00:03:40,190
Makanlah banyak sikit.

25
00:03:44,510 --> 00:03:45,350
Panas!

26
00:03:47,860 --> 00:03:48,700
Awak cepatlah rasa,

27
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:49,570
macam mana rasanya?

28
00:03:58,460 --> 00:03:59,300
Tak sedap?

29
00:04:01,350 --> 00:04:02,420
Saya baru sedar terdapat semua ini.

30
00:04:03,990 --> 00:04:04,860
Daun saderi,

31
00:04:05,300 --> 00:04:06,140
kek kacang pain,

32
00:04:06,140 --> 00:04:07,550
kek bijan dan juga gula batu.

33
00:04:07,550 --> 00:04:08,390
Sangat wangi!

34
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:09,580
Kenapa awak tak dapat rasakannya?

35
00:04:10,140 --> 00:04:11,070
Kalau macam tu, lain kali saya...

36
00:04:11,070 --> 00:04:11,920
Jangan.

37
00:04:11,930 --> 00:04:12,770
Jangan ada lain kali lagi.

38
00:04:13,420 --> 00:04:14,260
Lepaskanlah saya.

39
00:04:19,860 --> 00:04:20,710
Kalau macam tu, awak habiskanlah

40
00:04:20,710 --> 00:04:21,590
apa yang sudah awak gigit itu.

41
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:25,300
Habiskannya.

42
00:04:34,550 --> 00:04:35,390
Sedap tak?

43
00:04:52,470 --> 00:04:53,380
Awak marahkah?

44
00:04:59,350 --> 00:05:00,500
Awak tak nak bercakap dengan saya lagi?

45
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:03,300
♪Musim bunga tiba, ais dan salji mencair♪

46
00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:04,260
Kalau macam tu, minta maaf pada saya.

47
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:07,590
Saya tak buat salah apa pun.

48
00:05:07,590 --> 00:05:08,860
Saya sudah buat ini sepanjang petang.

49
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:11,940
Awak ini memang...

50
00:05:14,710 --> 00:05:15,940
Tak bolehkah awak
mengalah sekali dengan saya?

51
00:05:20,670 --> 00:05:21,670
Baiklah.

52
00:05:22,710 --> 00:05:24,030
Lain kali saya takkan paksa awak makan

53
00:05:24,030 --> 00:05:25,260
benda yang awak tak nak makan lagi.

54
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:31,350
Macam itulah.

55
00:05:31,350 --> 00:05:34,590
♪Pinjam keindahan dunia♪

56
00:05:34,620 --> 00:05:35,470
Bulan purnama pertengahan musim luruh,

57
00:05:36,470 --> 00:05:37,380
mari kita pergi melihat bulan.

58
00:05:38,300 --> 00:05:39,470
Di Guixu, segala roh menangis hiba,

59
00:05:40,350 --> 00:05:41,940
awak tak pernah berpeluang
menikmati bulan purnama dengan tenang.

60
00:05:43,710 --> 00:05:45,380
Adakah kita sudah berbaik macam ni saja?

61
00:05:45,990 --> 00:05:46,830
Semudah itu?

62
00:05:48,940 --> 00:05:50,590
Saya sememangnya sangat senang dipujuk.

63
00:05:53,010 --> 00:06:01,090
♪Mendengar kata-kata yang gembira,
juga bersinar dengan terang♪

64
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:07,640
♪Minum seteko arak mimpi
dalam ratusan ribu tahun♪

65
00:06:09,370 --> 00:06:17,710
♪Biarpun hidupku singkat, aku
berani harungi keabadian bersama kau♪

66
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:19,740
Jualan buah hari ini agak bagus.

67
00:06:21,150 --> 00:06:22,550
Tak sia-sia saya berjalan sejauh ini.

68
00:06:22,550 --> 00:06:25,540
♪Nikmati keseronokan seketika♪

69
00:06:25,780 --> 00:06:33,040
♪Semoga hanyut dalam mimpi mabuk
agar ingatan kekal selama-lamanya♪

70
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:40,240
♪Tolong bawa aku menyeberang
kehidupan yang panjang ini♪

71
00:06:40,590 --> 00:06:41,940
Bukankah awak suka berperang?

72
00:06:43,060 --> 00:06:44,110
Bukankah awak tak takut mati?

73
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:47,150
Sekarang seluruh badan penuh luka,

74
00:06:48,590 --> 00:06:49,430
padan muka.

75
00:06:54,420 --> 00:06:55,260
Terima kasih.

76
00:07:00,300 --> 00:07:01,140
Peluklah saya.

77
00:07:13,860 --> 00:07:14,700
Si Musang Duan,

78
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:17,230
saya tak izinkan
apa-apa berlaku pada awak.

79
00:07:18,180 --> 00:07:19,020
Faham?

80
00:07:38,710 --> 00:07:40,350
Saya yang terlalu mementingkan diri,

81
00:07:41,910 --> 00:07:43,150
meninggalkan awak di dunia manusia,

82
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:45,940
kekal di sisi saya.

83
00:07:47,350 --> 00:07:48,470
Mesti ia sangat menyakitkan, bukan?

84
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:52,030
Saya suka menemani di sisi awak.

85
00:07:53,790 --> 00:07:55,420
Saya suka bersama dengan awak.

86
00:07:56,060 --> 00:07:57,740
Inilah hari-hari
paling bahagia buat saya.

87
00:08:00,710 --> 00:08:01,550
Puan sudah lahir,

88
00:08:04,260 --> 00:08:05,150
saya belum lahir.

89
00:08:06,420 --> 00:08:07,380
Puan belum berubah,

90
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:09,350
saya sudah tua.

91
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:13,230
Kesal kerana tidak pernah

92
00:08:15,740 --> 00:08:16,940
setiap hari bersama.

93
00:08:19,550 --> 00:08:20,390
Hari...

94
00:08:31,380 --> 00:08:32,430
Simu, jangan tepuk lagi.

95
00:08:34,310 --> 00:08:35,260
Saya takkan

96
00:08:36,380 --> 00:08:37,660
biarkan awak sendirian.

97
00:08:38,430 --> 00:08:40,020
Saya takkan biarkan awak

98
00:08:40,860 --> 00:08:41,700
keseorangan.

99
00:08:43,710 --> 00:08:44,550
Si Musang Duan,

100
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:45,980
tak apa.

101
00:08:46,900 --> 00:08:47,740
Tak apa.

102
00:09:03,310 --> 00:09:04,150
Tak apa.

103
00:09:06,260 --> 00:09:07,430
Awak tak perlu lagi

104
00:09:07,430 --> 00:09:08,470
hidup dalam penderitaan demi saya.

105
00:09:13,590 --> 00:09:15,070
Bolehlah pergi dengan tenang sekarang.

106
00:09:19,380 --> 00:09:20,230
Simu,

107
00:09:23,430 --> 00:09:24,470
minta maaf.

108
00:09:27,710 --> 00:09:28,660
Duan Shunxi,

109
00:09:31,540 --> 00:09:33,260
awak sudah melakukannya
dengan cukup baik.

110
00:09:36,310 --> 00:09:37,190
Benar.

111
00:09:39,110 --> 00:09:40,740
Terima kasih
kerana sentiasa menemani saya.

112
00:09:58,380 --> 00:09:59,220
Duan Xu.

113
00:10:05,990 --> 00:10:07,020
Si Musang Duan.

114
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:11,310
Duan Shunxi.

115
00:10:13,830 --> 00:10:14,740
Duan Shunxi,

116
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:17,660
saya tarik balik
apa yang saya katakan tadi.

117
00:10:17,660 --> 00:10:19,070
Janganlah pergi.

118
00:10:19,590 --> 00:10:20,500
Janganlah pergi.

119
00:10:22,070 --> 00:10:23,740
Jangan tinggalkan saya.

120
00:10:24,710 --> 00:10:25,780
Duan Shunxi,

121
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:28,780
janganlah pergi.

122
00:10:31,710 --> 00:10:34,230
Saya tarik balik
apa yang saya katakan tadi.

123
00:10:35,430 --> 00:10:37,260
Janganlah pergi.

124
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:26,140
(Segala perkara di dunia ini
berlalu dalam sekelip mata.)

125
00:11:28,620 --> 00:11:29,590
(Hanya saya)

126
00:11:31,990 --> 00:11:33,230
(yang tidak akan mati mahupun musnah.)

127
00:12:14,070 --> 00:12:15,020
Si Musang Duan.

128
00:12:31,990 --> 00:12:32,830
Duan Xu.

129
00:12:33,380 --> 00:12:34,220
Duan Xu,

130
00:12:35,050 --> 00:12:35,900
bangunlah.

131
00:12:35,900 --> 00:12:36,740
Duan Xu.

132
00:12:37,230 --> 00:12:38,070
Duan Xu.

133
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:50,580
Simu.

134
00:12:56,110 --> 00:12:56,950
Simu.

135
00:12:59,660 --> 00:13:00,500
Ini saya.

136
00:13:34,140 --> 00:13:35,860
Saya dapat memegang jantung awak lagi.

137
00:13:44,230 --> 00:13:45,070
Bagusnya.

138
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:49,190
He Simu sudah datang menjemput saya.

139
00:13:50,950 --> 00:13:52,740
Ini kali pertama dalam hidup saya,

140
00:13:56,740 --> 00:13:57,950
ada orang yang datang menjemput saya.

141
00:14:39,190 --> 00:14:40,830
Jiang Ai, apa niat awak sebenarnya?

142
00:14:41,310 --> 00:14:42,740
Mengapa Lilin Hati manusia itu terputus?

143
00:14:43,830 --> 00:14:45,830
Adakah awak berpakat dengan Bai Sanxing?

144
00:14:46,110 --> 00:14:47,070
Sekarang awak patut risau,

145
00:14:47,070 --> 00:14:48,140
jika Penguasa Roh tidak keluar,

146
00:14:48,140 --> 00:14:49,070
bagaimana kita mahu berhadapan

147
00:14:49,070 --> 00:14:49,910
dengan ketua dewan yang lain?

148
00:14:50,710 --> 00:14:52,020
Jika sesuatu terjadi kepada He Simu,

149
00:14:52,020 --> 00:14:53,190
saya pasti tidak akan melepaskan awak.

150
00:15:16,950 --> 00:15:18,540
Simu membahagikan Lilin Hatinya

151
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:19,990
untuk menyalakan semula nyawa Duan Xu.

152
00:15:27,420 --> 00:15:30,620
(Astaka Zhaomu, Guixu)

153
00:16:05,830 --> 00:16:06,670
Duan Xu,

154
00:16:09,830 --> 00:16:11,140
boleh dengar suara saya?

155
00:16:36,620 --> 00:16:37,710
Apa yang awak impikan?

156
00:17:16,150 --> 00:17:17,190
Si Musang Duan,

157
00:17:18,430 --> 00:17:19,950
saya tidak suka awak begini.

158
00:17:23,670 --> 00:17:24,780
Cepatlah bangun.

159
00:18:01,740 --> 00:18:03,710
Yan.

160
00:18:04,430 --> 00:18:06,540
Yan, dengan adanya awak di Guixu,

161
00:18:07,150 --> 00:18:09,060
saya boleh tinggal
di dunia manusia beberapa hari lagi.

162
00:18:28,100 --> 00:18:28,940
Jangan bergerak.

163
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:30,300
Kuasa roh awak
sudah terlalu banyak susut.

164
00:18:46,630 --> 00:18:48,150
Dia bukan sekadar manusia biasa.

165
00:18:48,390 --> 00:18:49,540
Dia ialah pasangan ikatan mantera saya,

166
00:18:49,540 --> 00:18:50,630
dialah milik saya.

167
00:18:51,430 --> 00:18:52,390
Saya mahu dia hidup,

168
00:18:52,990 --> 00:18:54,020
maka dia tidak boleh mati.

169
00:19:08,950 --> 00:19:09,820
Perjumpaan pagi ini

170
00:19:10,060 --> 00:19:12,260
diadakan betul-betul di hadapan
pintu balai peraduan Penguasa Roh.

171
00:19:12,910 --> 00:19:14,500
Ini sesuatu yang belum pernah berlaku.

172
00:19:15,100 --> 00:19:16,780
Nampaknya nafsu
sudah membutakan fikiran.

173
00:19:18,910 --> 00:19:19,910
Awal-awal pagi lagi,

174
00:19:19,910 --> 00:19:20,780
kita sudah menerima perutusan

175
00:19:20,780 --> 00:19:22,580
daripada Penguasa Roh
untuk menukar lokasi perjumpaan.

176
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:24,340
Apa yang dah berlaku?

177
00:19:24,740 --> 00:19:26,260
Mungkin ada kena-mengena
dengan manusia itu.

178
00:19:30,670 --> 00:19:31,990
Perkara begini pun
Perdana Menteri Kanan boleh bersabar?

179
00:19:42,060 --> 00:19:42,900
Perdana Menteri Kanan sudah tiba.

180
00:19:43,740 --> 00:19:45,260
- Perdana Menteri Kanan.
- Perdana Menteri Kanan.

181
00:19:45,260 --> 00:19:46,740
- Perdana Menteri Kanan.
- Perdana Menteri Kanan.

182
00:19:57,780 --> 00:19:58,820
Mengapa Perdana Menteri Kiri
tidak datang?

183
00:19:59,500 --> 00:20:01,230
Mungkin juga
ada kaitan dengan manusia itu.

184
00:20:16,260 --> 00:20:17,100
Penguasa Roh,

185
00:20:17,230 --> 00:20:18,580
semua ketua dewan sudah berkumpul.

186
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:28,740
Kebelakangan ini,
semua menteri telah bekerja keras

187
00:20:28,740 --> 00:20:30,670
untuk menguruskan hal
roh merayau yang mencapai nirwana.

188
00:20:31,950 --> 00:20:33,950
Namun ada pihak yang memalsukan rekod

189
00:20:34,260 --> 00:20:35,390
semata-mata untuk
melengkapkan undang-undang.

190
00:20:37,430 --> 00:20:38,820
- Ampun, Puan.
- Ampun, Puan.

191
00:20:39,190 --> 00:20:40,500
- Puan, mohon ampuni kami.
- Puan, mohon ampuni kami.

192
00:20:41,100 --> 00:20:42,740
Perkara ini sudah dihukum
oleh Perdana Menteri Kanan,

193
00:20:43,630 --> 00:20:44,820
maka saya tidak akan
memanjangkannya lagi.

194
00:21:02,950 --> 00:21:03,790
Jika ada yang berani berkhianat lagi,

195
00:21:04,340 --> 00:21:05,190
kamu akan musnah selama-lamanya.

196
00:21:05,630 --> 00:21:06,820
Jika tiada apa-apa lagi, bersurailah.

197
00:21:07,990 --> 00:21:09,470
- Baik, Puan.
- Baiklah.

198
00:21:09,470 --> 00:21:10,500
- Mari kita pergi.
- Mari kita pergi.

199
00:21:25,300 --> 00:21:26,140
Penguasa Roh,

200
00:21:26,470 --> 00:21:27,470
saya memohon untuk menghadap.

201
00:21:34,540 --> 00:21:35,380
Bercakaplah dari luar pintu.

202
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:38,630
Manusia fana itu
ada di balai peraduan awak.

203
00:21:41,190 --> 00:21:42,260
Apa kaitannya dengan awak?

204
00:21:43,400 --> 00:21:44,260
Jadi, Penguasa Roh,

205
00:21:44,260 --> 00:21:45,470
adakah disebabkan manusia fana itu,

206
00:21:45,470 --> 00:21:47,300
awak menukar tempat
perjumpaan pagi hari ini?

207
00:21:48,340 --> 00:21:49,780
Awak sedang menyoal saya?

208
00:21:50,190 --> 00:21:51,100
Saya tidak berani.

209
00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:52,780
Cuma manusia fana ini

210
00:21:52,780 --> 00:21:54,190
bukan sahaja menceroboh
Penjara Ilusi Sembilan Petak,

211
00:21:54,470 --> 00:21:55,500
malah turut mengikat awak, Penguasa Roh.

212
00:21:55,820 --> 00:21:57,060
Ini membuatkan orang lain berfikir

213
00:21:57,060 --> 00:21:58,260
bahawa awak leka dengan hiburan

214
00:21:58,390 --> 00:21:59,230
dan mengabaikan urusan rasmi.

215
00:21:59,540 --> 00:22:00,500
Hari ini pun

216
00:22:00,990 --> 00:22:02,710
para ketua dewan sudah mula merungut.

217
00:22:03,150 --> 00:22:04,260
Jika perkara ini berlarutan,

218
00:22:04,710 --> 00:22:05,630
akibatnya tidak dapat dibayangkan.

219
00:22:06,150 --> 00:22:07,300
Jika mereka tidak berpuas hati,

220
00:22:07,910 --> 00:22:08,990
bunuh sahaja mereka.

221
00:22:09,780 --> 00:22:10,620
Yan Ke,

222
00:22:11,540 --> 00:22:12,820
sebenarnya mereka yang tidak puas hati,

223
00:22:12,820 --> 00:22:13,870
atau awak yang tidak puas hati?

224
00:22:14,260 --> 00:22:15,100
Simu,

225
00:22:15,340 --> 00:22:16,670
awak tahu saya tidak bermaksud begitu.

226
00:22:17,230 --> 00:22:18,670
Saya cuma memikirkan tentang awak.

227
00:22:18,820 --> 00:22:20,230
- Saya cuma...
- Awak cuma Perdana Menteri Kanan.

228
00:22:20,540 --> 00:22:21,910
Patuhi sahaja tugas awak.

229
00:22:22,390 --> 00:22:23,870
Jangan lakukan perkara
yang melampaui batas.

230
00:22:31,100 --> 00:22:32,780
Sebaik sahaja
dia melangkah masuk ke Guixu,

231
00:22:32,780 --> 00:22:33,620
dia sepatutnya sudah mati!

232
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:38,500
Penguasa Roh,
demi menjaga nama baik awak,

233
00:22:39,060 --> 00:22:40,390
izinkan saya bertindak melampaui batas.

234
00:22:51,470 --> 00:22:52,670
Jangan buat lagi.

235
00:23:08,100 --> 00:23:09,150
Sekadar seorang Perdana Menteri Kanan,

236
00:23:09,780 --> 00:23:11,150
patuhi sahaja tugas awak.

237
00:23:11,780 --> 00:23:13,150
Jangan lakukan
perkara yang melampaui batas.

238
00:23:13,630 --> 00:23:15,580
Sekadar seorang Perdana Menteri Kanan?

239
00:23:16,990 --> 00:23:18,630
Sekadar Perdana Menteri Kanan?

240
00:23:19,230 --> 00:23:20,150
Dalam hati awak,

241
00:23:20,150 --> 00:23:21,710
saya hanyalah seorang
Perdana Menteri Kanan?

242
00:24:21,740 --> 00:24:22,580
